description:
Phase 7 of Decked Out introduces the new difficulty "Deep Frost" which guarantees an artifact location down on the new Level 4. We spend a few runs having fun exploring it and also continue enjoying the card collecting aspect of the game.

This phase also brings out the rare Rage Etho. Unlucky mob AI combined with bad parkour skills are a deadly mix. More difficulty increases around the dungeon along with the new hardest level make this the deadliest phase for most of the Hermits.
